# PART 10 — Install PM2 (Optional but Recommended)

## Backend

```bash id="f8m4tr"
sudo npm install -g pm2
pm2 start server.js --name backend
pm2 save
```

---

## Frontend

```bash id="u1k9wc"
sudo npm install -g pm2
pm2 start npm --name frontend -- start
pm2 save
```

